      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAXIMUM PENALTY (7) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 2.25 lengths back in second (22.39) at this track in a Maiden over 390m. Can find winning form. PAW LONNIE (1) is a first starter by Yozo Bale out of Aratuza Bale with no trial form to work with. Gets his chance from the draw. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability. OUTLAW MOLLY (8) ran a nice race on debut when hitting the frame, finishing third (22.91) at this track over 390m. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. PAW YURI (2) is a Samantha Grenfell-trained newcomer by Amron Boy out of Fortuna Bale. Drawn well and should get his chance. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
